    <string name="faq_cat_general">General</string>
    <string name="faq_q_bg_play">How do I play music in the background?</string>
    <string name="faq_a_bg_play">DamonHole is designed to keep playing even when you leave the app or turn off your screen. Just start a song and you\'re good to go!</string>
    <string name="faq_q_screen_off">Does it work with the screen off?</string>
    <string name="faq_a_screen_off">Yes! You can lock your phone and the music will continue to play uninterrupted.</string>
    <string name="faq_q_stop_unexpectedly">Why did the music stop unexpectedly?</string>
    <string name="faq_a_stop_unexpectedly">This is usually due to battery optimization. Please ensure DamonHole is excluded from \'Battery Optimization\' in your phone settings.</string>
    <string name="faq_q_is_free">Is this really free?</string>
    <string name="faq_a_is_free">Yes, DamonHole allows you to enjoy music without any premium subscriptions.</string>
    <string name="faq_q_source">Where does the music come from?</string>
    <string name="faq_a_source">The app streams high-quality audio content from YouTube\'s vast library.</string>
    <string name="faq_q_download">Can I download songs for offline use?</string>
    <string name="faq_a_download">Currently, DamonHole focuses on providing the best streaming experience. Offline support may be considered for future updates.</string>
    <string name="faq_q_create_playlist">How do I create a playlist?</string>
    <string name="faq_a_create_playlist">Go to the \'Playlists\' tab and tap the \'+\' button at the top to create and name your new collection.</string>
    <string name="faq_q_add_to_playlist">How do I add songs to a playlist?</string>
    <string name="faq_a_add_to_playlist">While searching or viewing songs, tap the menu (three dots) next to a song and select \'Add to Playlist\'.</string>
    <string name="faq_q_change_theme">How do I change the app theme?</string>
    <string name="faq_a_change_theme">Go to Settings and use the \'Dark Mode\' switch to toggle between light and dark themes.</string>
    <string name="faq_q_audio_quality">Can I change the audio quality?</string>
    <string name="faq_a_audio_quality">The app automatically selects the best quality based on your internet connection to ensure smooth playback.</string>
